msgid ""
"**Rebels showed up in force at the meeting** - some staging a “die-in” at the entrance while seven other rebels locked-on inside the conference hall, and another rebel turned himself into a “[security kangaroo](https://twitter.com/LukasSchnermann/status/1225735510511038465?s=20)” and hopped across the conference floor.\n"
